2. **Server sends the full time, frontend does the typewriter** - The server sends the full time string every second, and the frontend animates it character by character.

I think option 2 is cleaner - the server sends the full time as a regular SSE event (every second), and the frontend handles the typewriter animation locally. This way the SSE connection is simpler and the typewriter effect is smoother.

